reviewText: Ren & Stimpy are at their stupidest in this hilarious video. You'll laugh as they get themselves in a twisted and outrageous situation. The animation is amazing and will keep your eyes glued to the T.V. set. This  cat and dog duo will have you spewing milk out of your nose as they try to  go along with everyday life. Only this everyday life is not what you'd  expect. Rest assured to expect however a hilarious time with Ren &  Stimpy.
